welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Fort Meade, a charming city known for its rich history and small-town charm. We invite you to explore and discover all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tipton AAF Airport serves commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Tipton AAF Airport handles all cargo and freight operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at BWI serves both domestic and international flights and houses all necessary services and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at BWI serves airlines such as Southwest, Alaska, and Spirit and offers a variety of dining and shopping options for passengers.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at BWI serves airlines such as American, Delta, and United and features a variety of amenities including lounges and duty-free shopping.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at BWI serves airlines such as JetBlue, Frontier, and Air Canada and offers a variety of services including currency exchange and pet relief areas.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Simply select the network and follow the prompts to connect.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lee Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lee Airport is reserved for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Glenn L Martin Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A

terminals.name: Terminal B/C

terminals.name: Terminal D

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial and private flights at Montgomery County Airport.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
